# Experiment scratch. The method, fixtures, harness and findings are tracked so
# the measurements cited in docs/ resolve for anyone who clones. The raw model
# transcripts are not: they are large, regenerable by re-running the harness, and
# their per-cell caching means a stale file silently substitutes for a real run.

.exp/**/results/
.exp/**/results2/
.exp/routing/rows*.json
.exp/routing/arena/

# J7 (tldr efficacy) predates the tracked-experiment convention and stays local.
.exp/tldr/
.exp/tldr_b/
.exp/tldr_c/
.exp/experiments.db
